OL,3,CMurder hunt under way after man
OL,4,Cstabbed in underpass
OL,6,FA 41-year-old man has died in hospital
OL,7,Fafter being stabbed in the chest in an
OL,8,Funderpass in Redditch.
OL,10,FPolice have launched a murder
OL,11,Finvestigation after the death of the
OL,12,Fvictim, who was found injured in the
OL,13,FWorcestershire town, at about 8.35am
OL,14,Fon Tuesday (28 April).
OL,16,FOfficers believe the stabbing took
OL,17,Fplace in the underpass which leads
OL,18,Ffrom Longdon Close to Martley Close
OL,19,Fand Woodrow Centre.
OL,21,FNo arrests have been made.
