OL,3,CMurder hunt under way after man
OL,4,Cstabbed in underpass
OL,6,FDetective Chief Inspector Gareth
OL,7,FLougher from West Mercia Police said:
OL,8,F"Officers were quickly deployed to a
OL,9,Freport of a stabbing in Redditch this
OL,10,Fmorning, where a man was found with a
OL,11,Flife-threatening injury.
OL,13,F"He sadly later passed away in
OL,14,Fhospital, and our thoughts are with
OL,15,Fhis family and loved ones at this
OL,16,Fdifficult time.
OL,18,F"Officers have been carrying out
OL,19,Fextensive enquiries since this
OL,20,Fmorning, including reviewing CCTV and
OL,21,Fconducting house to house visits."
